OL,3,C'We will be forever grateful':
OL,4,CMargaret Le Cras' SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FThe Channel Islands are marking a
OL,8,Fspecial milestone anniversary:
OL,9,Fcelebrating 80 years since the SS Vega
OL,10,Fdocked in Jersey and Guernsey harbours
OL,11,Fto deliver thousands of precious Red
OL,12,FCross parcels.
OL,14,FFrom December 1944, the relief ship
OL,15,Fdelivered more than 100,000 Red Cross
OL,16,Fparcels, helping to keep thousands
OL,17,Falive during the Occupation.
