OL,3,C'We will be forever grateful':
OL,4,CMargaret Le Cras' SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FMargaret was born in 1939 and grew up
OL,8,Fin Guernsey's countryside through the
OL,9,FGerman Occupation.
OL,11,FShe says: "I wouldn't have known we
OL,12,Fwere occupied, to me that was my life.
OL,14,F"I would have been shielded from a lot
OL,15,Fof what was going on and had a very
OL,16,Fsheltered childhood. I was too young
OL,17,Fto understand what the war was."
