OL,3,C'We will be forever grateful':
OL,4,CMargaret Le Cras' SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,F"It brought it home to me that they
OL,8,Fwere taking our onions. That was the
OL,9,Ffirst time I'd seen the Germans take
OL,10,Fanything from us."
OL,12,FBut it wasn't just food in short
OL,13,Fsupply: warmth was also hard to come
OL,14,Fby.
OL,16,FMargaret explains: "I remember we used
OL,17,Fto have to gather wood and
OL,18,Fspecifically pinecones.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
