OL,3,C'We will be forever grateful':
OL,4,CMargaret Le Cras' SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,FAnd the parcels from New Zealand held:
OL,9,FMargaret recalls: "Well (the parcels)
OL,10,Fcertainly saved Guernsey and Jersey
OL,11,Fwithout a doubt.
OL,13,F"I remember our parcel was a Canadian
OL,14,Fone but when we went back to school in
OL,15,FJanuary there were big discussions in
OL,16,Fthe playground as to who had the best
OL,17,Fparcels.
