OL,3,C'We will be forever grateful':
OL,4,CMargaret Le Cras' SS Vega memories 80
OL,5,Cyears on
OL,7,F"Some had had Canadian like we had and
OL,8,Fthe others had New Zealand ones and
OL,9,Falthough they had more or less the
OL,10,Fsame, it was different names and
OL,11,Fdifferent tins.
OL,13,F"There were big arguments about who
OL,14,Fhad the best parcels."
OL,16,F80 years on since Margaret received
OL,17,Fher first Red Cross parcel, the
OL,18,Fgratitude she felt that day remains.
